{{Expand Estonian|Martin Aagaard|date=September 2014}} [[File:Martin Aagaard - Skips i måneskinn.jpg|right|thumb| 300 px|''Skips i måneskinn'']] '''Zacharias Martin Aagaard''' (13 October 1863 – 1913), was a Norwegian painter. Aagaard specialized as [[marine painting]].<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.mutualart.com/Artist/Zackarais-Martin-Aagaard/4DA5837DE001F030 | title=Zackarais Martin Aagaard | publisher=mutualart.com | accessdate=September 25, 2014}}</ref>
==Early life== Martin Aagaard was born in [[Levanger]] in [[Nord-Trøndelag]] county, Norway. He was educated at [[Trondheim]] Technical School and the Royal Drawing School in [[Oslo]]. He was a student of [[Harriet Backer]] and [[Knud Bergslien]]. Additionally he apprenticed for a time with [[Christian Krohg]]. He spent time researching locations in [[Lofoten]] and [[Finnmark]].<ref>[https://nkl.snl.no/Martin_Aagaard ''Martin Aagaard, marinemaler'' (forfatter, Ingrid Reed Thomsen. Norsk kunstnerleksikon)]</ref>
He exhibited his works from 1898 in [[Bergen]]. He exhibited at the [[Exposition Universelle (1900)]]. Several of his paintings were executed in large dimensions. In 1909, Aagaard was in [[Trondheim]], where he painted a large painting from the harbor featuring pleasure crafts. His work is on public display at the [[Bergen]] Maritime Museum, [[Nordmøre Museum]], and [[Trondheim]] Maritime Museum among other locations.<ref>[http://www.fineartemporium.com/se-Aagaard.htm ''Aagaard, Martin Zacharias'' (Karsten Buchholz KG.)]</ref>
==Medium== Aagaard worked with oils on large canvas.
==Works== In recent years, Aagaard's work has sold at auction between $438USD for 'Ångare', and $11,929USD for 'Norske Båter Langs Kysten'.<ref>http://www.findartinfo.com/english/list-prices-by-artist/136412/zackarais-martin-aagaard.html</ref>
==Gallery== <gallery > Aagaard-martin-1863-1913-norwa-setting-sail-from-the-fjords-a.jpg|''Umbes'' (1880) Aagaard-martin-1863-1913-norwa-for-fulle-seil.jpg|''For fulle seil'' Aagaard-martin-1863-1913-norwa-skibsmotiv-med-klippebaggrund.jpg|''Sjølandskap med fjellformasjoner'' File:Martin Aagaard - Seilskute Og Dampskip.jpg|''Seilskute Og Dampskip'' (1886) File:Martin Aagaard - Tyskerbryggen I Bergen.jpg|''Tyskerbryggen i Bergen'' (1886) Martin Aagaard - Sailor med kikkert.jpg|''Sailor med kikkert'' Aagaard-martin-1863-1913-norwa-borren.jpg|''Borøen'' (1900) </gallery>
